<template>
{{ response }}
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'

export default {
    data(){
        return {
            response: "",
        }
    },
mounted: function() {
 this.getArticles();
},
    name: 'ShowDataBase',
    method:{
        async getArticles() {
            const endpoint = "/api/v1/image/";
            this.response = await axios.get(endpoint);
        },
    }
    }
</script>
